能看下你filter的实现吗？
问题点应该在于你没有透传baggage
``` java
@Configuration
@Import({ DelegatingTracingFilter.class, SpanCustomizingAsyncHandlerInterceptor.class })
public class WebZipkinConfig implements WebMvcConfigurer {

	@Resource
	private SpanCustomizingAsyncHandlerInterceptor interceptor;

	@Resource
	private Tracing tracing;

	@Override
	public void addInterceptors(InterceptorRegistry registry) {
		registry.addInterceptor(interceptor);
	}

	@Bean
	public HttpTracing httpTracing() {
		return HttpTracing.create(tracing);
	}
}
```
这块内容的代码看起来应该只能在rest 下生效,他对dubbo 是无效的

@conghuhu 集成Zipkin怎么实现只有一个Trace ID呢？

我是参考https://cn.dubbo.apache.org/zh-cn/blog/2018/06/17/%E5%9C%A8-dubbo-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-zipkin这篇文章集成的

用的集成项目是https://github.com/openzipkin/brave/tree/master/instrumentation/dubbo

I add two compatible method and repackage jar, then it works. 

CompatibleInvoker.java add method:
```java
@Override
public org.apache.dubbo.rpc.Result invoke(org.apache.dubbo.rpc.Invocation invocation) throws org.apache.dubbo.rpc.RpcException {
    return new Result.CompatibleResult(invoker.invoke(invocation));
}
```

CompatibleResult.java add method:
```java
@Override
public org.apache.dubbo.rpc.Result whenCompleteWithContext(BiConsumer<org.apache.dubbo.rpc.Result, Throwable> fn) {
    return delegate.whenCompleteWithContext(fn);
}
```
